OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FGovernment plans to force  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Flandlords to tackle mould  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Rogue social housing landlords could be
OL,6, forced to repair mouldy homes within 24
OL,7, hours as part of government proposals  
OL,8, after a toddler's death four years ago.
OL,10,FCampaigners have demanded reforms after
OL,11,Ftwo-year-old Awaab Ishak died from     
OL,12,Fmould exposure at his Rochdale home in 
OL,13,F2020.                                  
OL,15,FThe proposals would see new time limits
OL,16,Fset for repairs to unsafe homes.       
OL,18,FHousing Secretary Michael Gove said the
OL,19,F"strong, robust action" would help     
OL,20,F"prevent tragedies".                   
